data.description: Don't miss out on seeing this beautifully updated home in Littlefield, TX! This house features three spacious bedrooms and two bathrooms. The master bedroom is isolated and includes sliding barndoors to the master bathroom. Both bathrooms are complete with double vanities and updated countertops. The kitchen is newly remodeled and features lots of cabinet space great for storage. The living room is a great size and features a brick fireplace, perfect to cozy-up by on those cold winter nights. The home has been updated with newer flooring throughout, newer windows, and a newer roof. The refrigerator will convey.  If you love the outdoors, you will enjoy this large, beautiful backyard. It is landscaped with lush green grass, a covered patio, a lighted pergola, a newer fence, a huge above ground pool with a sand pump, and a 24x24 workshop with a garage door into the alley.
